Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:05.09,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在找一个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm looking for a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:09.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,你明白什么叫地方吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you understand the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.66,0:04:19.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,有三个人分别给了我那地方的坐标\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Three people have given me coordinates to that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,其中两份是吻合的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Two of the coordinates match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你会怎么做  理查德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What would you do, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,我会去查那处两份吻合的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'd check out the two that match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:34.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,你真是个聪明的年轻人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a very bright young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们就快到达吻合的那个地方了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And we're very close to the two that match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,这显示就在那上面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It says it's right up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:45.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们要上去吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're going up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:47.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在就上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're going up there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:15.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,是人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:02.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dear God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:21.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,我打赌就在那岩石上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll bet it's right up there on that rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:32.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,我比你老25岁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm 25 years your senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:34.87,*Default,,0,0,0,,拿着这个  上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take this and get on up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果接近了就会发出嘀嘀声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It'll beep when you're close
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果到了地方就会持续作响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And make a continuous tone when you're on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我你发现了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me know what you find.
