Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.54,*Default,,0,0,0,,别让人看到  盯着这房子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Over there out of sight and stake out this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:02.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:03.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come here.
