Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,道吉不会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, Dougie's not gonna do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:24.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈  昏迷跟电有关吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mom, does a coma have something to do with electricity?
